@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.40
    tmp = (v0 + 0.70)
    v1 = 0.73
    v2 = (v2 - ((v0 + 0.14 / v1 + 0.65) * 0.72))
    tmp = (tmp / ((tmp + 0.95 / v1 + 0.74) - 0.27))
    data[tid] = v0
